  "detailed_description": "<strong>Cat Dungeon Escape is a hard challenging Puzzle Game with some precision platform elements!! </strong><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/22030a4f8972a8becf633fbba4c19267.poster.avif?t=1629742225\" width=300 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/22030a4f8972a8becf633fbba4c19267.webm?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/22030a4f8972a8becf633fbba4c19267.mp4?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rotate the Scene and invert the gravity for to get the key , open the door and escape !! <br>With several traps along the way, this can be more difficult than you think !!!</strong><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/d7a7016d2a3676d9adfad841c353c65d.poster.avif?t=1629742225\" width=450 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/d7a7016d2a3676d9adfad841c353c65d.webm?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/d7a7016d2a3676d9adfad841c353c65d.mp4?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  <br><strong>HARD CHALLENGING PUZZLE WITH PRECISION PLATFORM ELEMENTS</strong><br>The first levels are simple just to get used to the idea of ​​the game , and than it is getting hard level by level.. Perfect for Hard Game Lovers<br>To take the key will be not so simple !! Fire traps , spikes , portals and more are waiting for you !!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/44421b49289187985854473d34c5a5a5.poster.avif?t=1629742225\" width=480 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/44421b49289187985854473d34c5a5a5.webm?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/44421b49289187985854473d34c5a5a5.mp4?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br>The Gameplay is really simple and easy !! Use the keys  \"A\" and \"D\" to rotate screen and \"SPACE\" to invert gravity !!! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/bf36bf3472528361e86f11dcb0f256ed.poster.avif?t=1629742225\" width=450 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/bf36bf3472528361e86f11dcb0f256ed.webm?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645950/extras/bf36bf3472528361e86f11dcb0f256ed.mp4?t=1629742225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Manipulate gravity</li><li>Rotate scene</li><li>Easy gameplay </li><li>The challenge increases with each level </li><li>Pixel Art Game</li><li>Challenging Puzzle </li><li>50 Levels </li><li>Precision platform elements</li></ul>",
